            "data": {
                "description": {
                    "value": "The basidirond releases a cloud of invisible spores in a 20-foot emanation. Each creature in the area must succeed at a DC 22 Fortitude save or experience powerful hallucinations as long as it remains in the cloud, plus an additional 1d4 rounds after leaving the area. A creature must attempt a new save each round it remains within the area. The cloud persists for 5 rounds unless dispersed before then by a strong wind. Each hallucinating creature rolls 1d6 each round to determine what it hallucinates that round. <br><b>1 </b>The target is sinking in quicksand. It falls @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.Prone] and spends 1 action on its next turn flailing its limbs as if attempting to swim. <br><b>2 </b>The target is attacked by a swarm of spiders. It spends 2 actions on its next turn attacking the floor with a melee weapon (drawing a weapon if needed). It is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.Flat-Footed] against all attacks. <br><b>3 </b>An item the target is holding turns into a viper. The target @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.wQYmDStjdjn0I26t]{Release} the item and spends its next turn fleeing from it. <br><b>4 </b>The target is suffocating. It holds its breath and is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.Stunned] 3. <br><b>5</b> The target shrinks to 1/10 its normal size. For 1 round it is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.Slowed] 2 and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.Enfeebled] 4, and takes a -10-foot status penalty to its Speed. <br><b>6</b> The target is melting. It drops everything it's holding and becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.Slowed] 2 and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.Clumsy] 4 for 1 round.",
